    <date day="05" month="March" year="2020"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>   This document specifies extensions to the QUIC protocol to enable the
   simultaneous usage of multiple paths for a single connection.  The
   proposed extensions remain compliant with the current single-path
   QUIC design and preserve the QUIC privacy features.

	 </t>
